{"tid":2188043,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(真全民檢測) 李嘉誠投資家用病毒快速檢測儀　數十元全家人共用10月面世","createTime":"2020-09-04T04:14:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T15:08:07.000Z","uid":522,"like":114,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"e614f1d32532c9f1d570fbf776d6760123c4a3e4","tid":2188043,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/EeQq3WAWsAMC8hE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2FEeQq3WAWsAMC8hE.jpg&h=42421f72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日李嘉誠旗下維港投資創辦人周凱旋透露，維港投資正資助一間科技公司 Homodeus 對武漢肺炎相關的快速病毒檢測儀器研究，而相關儀器將會於今年 10 月面世，正努力爭取香港成為首輪受惠名單地區。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/920x920-694x356.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F920x920-694x356.jpg&h=45b0af26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n維港投資創辦人周凱旋在接受訪問時提到維港投資正以資助形式支援一間科技公司 Homodeus 進行與武漢肺炎相關的快速病毒檢測儀器研究，而相關儀器預料今年 10 月面世。她表示正努力向該公司爭取香港成為首輪受惠名單地區，並冀望這個項目能夠為為市民帶來廉價、快速而準確的測試。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/Packaging-694x390.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2FPackaging-694x390.png&h=018fc2f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她指這部快速病毒檢測儀器能夠讓用家放在家中，全家共用一個機器，並只需購入每個數十元的儀器便能為全家人作快速檢測，而且不限時間日子，「喜歡甚麼時候驗都可以」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/118599170_372419237257193_4037300774923292665_n-694x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F118599170_372419237257193_4037300774923292665_n-694x390.jpg&h=8aa5f864&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她又提到該儀器使用的恆溫技術名為 LAMP（Loop-mediated Isothermal Amplification，環介導等溫擴增），並指檢測速度比 PCR（聚合酶連鎖反應）更快，可直接快速檢驗樣本中是否存在病毒的遺傳物質，來判斷是否確診，而此測試目前在準確性，及避免假陽性、假陰性結果上有相當成果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/09/03/horizons-ventures-coronavirus-quick-test-oct-launch/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F09%2F03%2Fhorizons-ventures-coronavirus-quick-test-oct-launch%2Flife-tech%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cRAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=b4caefd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/09/03/horizons-ventures-coronavirus-quick-test-oct-launch/life-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"ca43d2c9f905f38d1c5e20eb73178df1e68f150c","tid":2188043,"uid":162535,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:16:33.000Z","msg":"等睇全民檢測rap<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af21c171b8afb80627afeedfec43f77f35a83dda","tid":2188043,"uid":15605,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:16:37.000Z","msg":"誠哥都次次追住港共黎咬"},{"pid":"3e760f54d2d826c75351decd10e4382e66189767","tid":2188043,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:18:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b0604da261a8061d5aa33fe6f73d348f9d8effd","tid":2188043,"uid":14103,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:25:04.000Z","msg":"好玩喎依部野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實學校一早要整部俾學生玩下啦 當培養下興趣 咁多學生 總會巿一兩個對病毒學興趣啦掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔駛搞到依家大眾咩係飛沫傳染又唔明 咩係黏膜又唔明 咩係土抗體又唔明 咩係免疫反應又唔明 一尾淨係識驚"},{"pid":"1036226e241736753dbeb30967bbb8009d121955","tid":2188043,"uid":89641,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8b0604da261a8061d5aa33fe6f73d348f9d8effd","tid":2188043,"uid":14103,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:25:04.000Z","msg":"好玩喎依部野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實學